--- dcmtk-3.6.6/dcmjpls/apps/CMakeLists.txt.orig	2021-08-28 22:06:28.200993561 +0200
+++ dcmtk-3.6.6/dcmjpls/apps/CMakeLists.txt	2021-08-29 12:52:13.793079185 +0200
